# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================

# 1. Run the setup_snowflake_user.sql script in Snowflake as ACCOUNTADMIN
# 2. Generate your private key if you haven't already:
#    openssl genrsa 2048 | openssl pkcs8 -topk8 -inform PEM -out snowflake_rsa_key.pem -nocrypt
# 3. Extract the public key:
#    openssl rsa -in snowflake_rsa_key.pem -pubout -out snowflake_rsa_key.pub
# 4. Update the RSA_PUBLIC_KEY in the SQL script with your public key
